00:42:32.196 --> 00:42:33.656
-[bumuntong hininga]
-[nagsisimula ang makina]

00:42:34.657 --> 00:42:36.200
Malatang it is.

00:42:42.582 --> 00:42:45.334
[news anchor over TV] Byeon Jongsik,
ex-mayor ng Yongdu

00:42:45.418 --> 00:42:48.337
at posibleng kandidato sa pagkapangulo,
pinaghihinalaan ng katiwalian.

00:42:48.421 --> 00:42:50.464
Sinasabi ng ulat na ang Beauté Group

00:42:50.548 --> 00:42:53.885
iligal na nag-lobby sa kanya para makakuha
