[Tatay ni Sungwoo] Niloloko mo ba ako?

00:43:42.558 --> 00:43:43.726
Oh, hindi ang aking likod.

00:43:43.809 --> 00:43:45.144
May buto ka lang diyan.

00:43:45.228 --> 00:43:46.646
[ungol]

