[golf club clatters sa sahig]

00:43:53.027 --> 00:43:54.278
Hiniling mong makita ako, ginoo?

00:44:02.995 --> 00:44:03.996
[sinara ang pinto]

00:44:05.122 --> 00:44:06.374
[Tatay ni Sungwoo] Ang insidente ng mayor.

00:44:07.041 --> 00:44:08.793
Ayusin mo, Sanghyeon.

00:44:09.710 --> 00:44:11.212
Makakarinig ka mula sa isang tagausig.

00:44:11.295 --> 00:44:13.965
OFFICE NG CEO

00:44:14.048 --> 00:44:15.508
[♪ tense na tumutugtog ng musika]

