00:44:44.036 --> 00:44:45.830
8TH DAEJU GENERAL HOSPITAL
COMMUNITY CARE DAY

00:44:45.913 --> 00:44:47.665
-[doktor 3] Sabihin ang "ah."
-[bata] Apat.

